    "tutorialText": [
        "Your goal is to keep the plant healthy as long as possible, harvesting the fruit that grows to reach a high score.",
        "The status bars above the plant represent water, light, fruit growth, and overall health. Health will improve over time as long as water, light, and hazards are managed.",
        "The tools on the right allow managing water and light levels. Select a tool by tapping it and use it by tapping on the plant. Most of the tools won't do anything right now.",
        "The drain and watering can tools (the second row) will decrease and increase the water level, respectively.",
        "If the water level is too low OR too high, the plant will lose health. Use the tools in the second row to keep the plant at a healthy water level.",
        "Light works similarly to water. The black hole and lamp tools (the third row) will decrease and increase the light level, respectively.",
        "Weather changes every few seconds. A preview of upcoming weather can be seen in the top right.",
        "As long as the plant is not losing health, it will grow fruit periodically. When the fruit turns red, it can be harvested with the basket tool.",
        "Your score is shown in the top left. It will regularly increase based on the current health of the plant. Whenever you harvest a fruit, you receive 100 bonus points.",
        "Periodically, hazards will spawn and approach your plant. If they reach the plant they will damage its health until they are defeated.",
        "The remaining tools can be used to defeat hazards. Each tool corresponds with one type of hazard, and the tool will be highlighted when that hazard spawns.",
        "For example, the scarecrow tool defeats the bird hazard. Use the scarecrow tool to defeat the bird.",
        "The weedkiller tool defeats the weed hazard.",
        "The pesticide tool defeats the bug hazard.",
        "The dog tool defeats the bunny hazard.",
        "The hammer tool defeats the mole hazard.",
        "The missile tool defeats the meteor hazard. If the meteor reaches the plant, it will explode and cause the plant to lose a lot of health.",
        "Tutorial complete! Keep your plant healthy, manage hazards, and harvest fruit! Click Next to return to the main menu."
    ],

